{"product_id":"brightening-cream-whitening-cream","title":"Brightening Cream (Whitening Cream)","description":"\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eNutriafresh Skin Brightening Cream is the best fairness cream that lightens the pigmented spots and brightens skin with its pigment-lightening agents like Vitamin C (MAP), Alpha Arbutin, Licorice Extract, and Kojic Acid dipalmitate.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eNutriafresh Skin Brightening Cream in Pakistan step-up the skin brightening action with the super stable derivative of vitamin C (Magnesium Ascorbyl Phosphate), delivers constant doses of vitamin C and improves the skin barrier intact and brightened. Its skin-neutral pH lowers the chances of skin sensitivity and discomfort, thus making Nutriafresh the best fairness cream in Pakistan.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"code-block code-block-4 ai-viewport-1\"\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eFactors like excess sun exposure, environmental factors, and pregnancy may develop darker skin patches and spots on the skin. Its size, color, and location vary, which makes it either Freckles or Melasma. Other than that, acne may also be responsible for the dark spots that appear after acne or pimple disappears. To treat bothering pigmented spots and darkened skin tone, use Nutriafresh Skin Brightening Cream in Pakistan. It treats common skin hyperpigmentation problems like dark skin tone, Melasma, Freckles, and Acne Marks.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eThe Safriderm range offers a natural, safe, and effective skin-brightening solution. Other than Skin Brightening Cream, Antiaging Antioxidant C Cream, and Skin Brightening Face Wash complete the whole skin brightening routine.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIndications:\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eNutriafresh, the best fairness cream specially formulated to reduce t